import React from 'react';
import {Form} from "formik";
import {Button, Col, Row} from '@themesberg/react-bootstrap';
import {InputField} from "../../components/form";
import {FontAwesomeIcon} from "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome";
import {faSave, faUndo} from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";

const CountryForm = () => {

	return (
		<Form>
			<Row>
				<Col md={12} className="mb-20">
					<InputField
						label="Country Name"
						name="countryName"
						type="text"
						placeholder="Enter Country Name"
					/>
				</Col>
				<Col md={12} className="mb-20">
					<InputField
						label="Country Name (Bn)"
						name="countryNameBn"
						type="text"
						placeholder="Enter Country Name (Bn)"
					/>
				</Col>
				<Col md={12} className="mb-20">
					<InputField
						label="Country Id Legacy"
						name="countryIdLegacy"
						type="text"
						placeholder="Enter Country Id Legacy"
					/>
				</Col>
				<Col md={12} className="mb-10 mt-10">
					<Button variant="success" className="f-right" type="submit">
						<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faSave} className="me-2"/> Submit
					</Button>
					<Button variant="dark" className="f-right mr-10" type="reset">
						<FontAwesomeIcon icon={faUndo} className="me-2"/> Reset
					</Button>
				</Col>
			</Row>
		</Form>
	);

};

export default CountryForm;
